Matthew B. Seiyefa, the most senior Director in the Department of State Services (DSS), will act as Director-General until further notice. This was announced by Laolu Akande, the spokesperson of the acting President, Prof. Yemi Osinbajo, via his Twitter handle. Seiyefa's appointment was sequel to the termination of the appointment of the Director General of the DSS Lawan Daura by the acting president.